<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="a16Jul1936"><font color="red">16 July 1936</font> <i>NLJL</i> (from Paul L&eacute;on to John Lane The Bodley Head): I beg to enclose reply to the first batch of your queries. I have just received the second and will answer it tomorrow. I am very glad about the meticulous way in which you establish your text and I take up every individual query with Mr Joyce. </div>
